title: Report of strange humming sound near old power station
text: Multiple residents reported a low-frequency humming sound originating from the abandoned Monongahela Power Station last night. Police investigated but found no signs of entry or active machinery. EMF readings were reportedly off the charts.

title: Local Farmer's Prize Cow Found... In a Tree
text: Jedidiah Smith, a farmer known for his prize-winning cattle, found his prized cow 'Bessie' inexplicably located in the high branches of an oak tree this morning. There were no tracks, and the animal was unharmed but clearly distressed.

title: Library Books on Arcane Symbols Vanish Overnight
text: The entire 'Occult & Ancient Symbols' section of the public library was found empty this morning. Security footage shows the books simply vanishing from the shelves around 3:00 AM. The night watchman reports feeling an unusual chill.

title: Man Reports His Reflection Grinned At Him
text: A local man was taken in for observation after frantically reporting that his own reflection in his bathroom mirror grinned at him independently. He later smashed the mirror. This is the third such report in the tri-county area this month.

title: Strange Lights Over Lake Erie
text: Residents along the shores of Lake Erie reported seeing a series of bright, pulsating lights in the sky last night. Witnesses described the lights as moving in a synchronized pattern before disappearing into the clouds.

title: Mysterious Crop Circles Appear Overnight
text: A farmer in rural Ohio discovered intricate crop circles in his cornfield this morning. The patterns are unlike any seen before, with some claiming they resemble ancient runes. Local authorities are investigating.
